{"word":"κάπριος","slug":"κάπριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κάπριος</b></el> <el>(κάπριος, ὁ,) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a wild boar</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; also, <el>σῦς κάπριος</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <a href='S:κάπρος'><el>κάπρος</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a> <el>κάπριος, ον</el>, <i>like a wild boar</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}